main ingredient for maiking chakli is rice flour.

00:00:12.956 --> 00:00:19.025
we can use moong dal flour, urhad dal flour and gram flour along with rice flour.

00:00:19.130 --> 00:00:22.654
else mix all the four ingredientsto make chakli

00:00:22.755 --> 00:00:26.541
toady we will mix ll the ingredients to make chakli

00:00:26.776 --> 00:00:31.799
lets see what all other ingredients are required to make chakli:

00:00:32.528 --> 00:00:34.885
rice flour - 1 cup

00:00:35.579 --> 00:00:37.849
oil - 1/3 cup

00:00:38.336 --> 00:00:40.241
gram flour - 1/2 cup

00:00:40.616 --> 00:00:42.664
urhad dal flour - 1/2 cup

00:00:42.817 --> 00:00:44.856
moong dal flour - 1/2 cup

00:00:45.207 --> 00:00:48.247
asafoetida - less tha 1/4 tsp

00:00:48.401 --> 00:00:50.576
cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:50.777 --> 00:00:53.325
carom seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:53.557 --> 00:00:55.533
seasame seeds - 1tbsp

00:00:55.950 --> 00:00:58.323
red chilly powder - 1/2 tsp

00:00:58.642 --> 00:01:01.721
salt - to taste or 1/2 tsp

00:01:02.146 --> 00:01:04.090
oil - to fry chakli

00:01:04.290 --> 00:01:06.234
lets start with the procedure of maing chakli:

00:01:06.364 --> 00:01:10.689
firstly we will knead dough

00:01:14.942 --> 00:01:19.034
take rice flour in a big bowl

00:01:20.430 --> 00:01:21.287
also add gram flour

00:01:24.121 --> 00:01:25.526
urhad dal flour

00:01:28.045 --> 00:01:29.688
moong dal flour

00:01:33.098 --> 00:01:34.122
sesame seeds

00:01:35.697 --> 00:01:36.840
carom seeds,

00:01:37.970 --> 00:01:39.232
salt

00:01:39.969 --> 00:01:41.318
asafoetida

00:01:42.267 --> 00:01:43.751
red chilly powder

00:01:44.722 --> 00:01:45.650
salt

00:01:48.546 --> 00:01:49.641
and oil in bowl

00:01:53.068 --> 00:01:56.711
mix all the ingredients nicely

00:02:04.989 --> 00:02:08.505
you can roast the all four cereals and prepare flour

00:02:09.059 --> 00:02:15.847
or else you can cook and grind the cereals and tehn mix them in the rice flour.

00:02:29.111 --> 00:02:34.344
now we will knead the dough with water

00:02:38.449 --> 00:02:42.441
the dough should be soft than puri's dough.

00:02:50.532 --> 00:02:55.631
now we will keep the dough aside for 20 minutes so that it gets plumpy.

00:03:05.378 --> 00:03:07.767
now we start making chakli

00:03:26.621 --> 00:03:33.745
take little amount of dough in your hands and roll it lengthwise.

00:03:51.943 --> 00:03:57.891
take on ploythene sheet and spread some oil on it so that it become soft

00:04:00.907 --> 00:04:05.050
place the round balls in the chakli machine maker.

00:04:24.622 --> 00:04:35.871
push the machine slowly,roll it like this givig a shape like that of chakli.

00:04:43.161 --> 00:04:46.843
prepare chakli and place it on polythene sheet first.

00:04:58.064 --> 00:05:02.461
give three roaunds and prepare chakli.

00:05:33.031 --> 00:05:35.896
now we will fry chakli on medium flame

00:05:55.760 --> 00:05:59.443
chakli have turned brown in colour and now we will take them out in a plate.

00:06:10.544 --> 00:06:12.640
crusty chakli is ready

